test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 2209 == 47
 +  where 2209 = <built-in function prod>([1, 47, 1, 47])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x72fdfe5f8bc0>([47])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x72fdfe5f8bc0> = [[1, 47, 1, 47, 1, 47], [1, 47, 1, 47, 1, 47], [47, 1, 47, 1, 47], [47, 1, 47, 1, 47], [1, 47, 1, 47], [1, 47, 1, 47], ...].count
